  "title": "Project Manager (Construction, M&E)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Oversee project execution, managing timelines and budgets to ensure timely completion.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with clients, vendors, subcontractors, and regulatory authorities for seamless project progress.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with site engineers to address any project-related challenges.</li>\n  <li>Ensure efficient operations and workflow throughout the project lifecycle.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Electrical Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li>At least 5 years as a <strong>Project Manager/M&amp;E Manager</strong> experience in the<strong> Construction Industry.</strong></li>\n  <li>Strong project management skills, including budgeting, scheduling, and coordination with stakeholders.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
